Add a "Add my own portrait" button on the website
Opens a form as a netlify function, where one can upload its own picture
Creates a PR on the repo with the "real" picture added
This might need to resize and compress the file
A hook


/api/portraitify
  take an image as text, return the portrait as text as well as the id
  if take an id, return a portrait as text

/api/submit
  take a real as text and a portrait as text
  also ask for github username
  create a PR with both files where the name is the github handle
  put the username as co-reviewer and ping it

